HOW TO EXTRACT THE JAR FILE
___________________________

At first download both the files Temperature Converter Tool.7z.001 and Temperature Converter Tool.7z.002 in a same location/folder.
Don't rename the files.
Now, go to the folder where you have downloaded.
Right click on "Temperature Converter Tool.7z.001" and hover 7-Zip.
In the 7-Zip menu, click Extract all.

